619
00:32:13,060 --> 00:32:13,900
Beiyue,

620
00:32:14,500 --> 00:32:15,900
I'm sorry.

621
00:32:18,220 --> 00:32:19,900
You were so young back then,

622
00:32:21,060 --> 00:32:22,660
and I left you behind.

623
00:32:25,660 --> 00:32:27,780
I'm so sorry about that.

624
00:32:29,420 --> 00:32:31,460
After I left you,

625
00:32:31,460 --> 00:32:33,660
I have been missing you every day.

626
00:32:34,220 --> 00:32:35,140
Beiyue,

627
00:32:39,380 --> 00:32:41,020
can you forgive me?

628
00:34:01,100 --> 00:34:01,940
Here.

629
00:34:10,020 --> 00:34:10,940
You can't drink alcohol.

630
00:34:12,780 --> 00:34:15,020
This is not alcohol. It's water.

631
00:34:15,020 --> 00:34:15,860
Just to fit the occasion.

632
00:34:22,460 --> 00:34:23,540
To fit the occasion.

633
00:35:08,140 --> 00:35:09,620
Aren't you here to persuade me?

634
00:35:12,220 --> 00:35:14,340
No, I'm not good at that.

635
00:35:16,780 --> 00:35:17,820
I don't have much experience

636
00:35:18,940 --> 00:35:20,140
in kinship.

637
00:35:22,580 --> 00:35:23,900
After all, I'm an orphan.

638
00:35:28,700 --> 00:35:29,940
What I mean is,

639
00:35:31,000 --> 00:35:32,020
in the Chancellor's Mansion,

640
00:35:33,020 --> 00:35:34,220
I felt like an orphan.

641
00:35:40,020 --> 00:35:40,980
Actually,

642
00:35:41,660 --> 00:35:42,740
I quite envy you.

643
00:35:47,620 --> 00:35:48,620
Not everyone

644
00:35:50,140 --> 00:35:51,740
gets a second chance.

645
00:36:08,540 --> 00:36:09,820
Let everything go as it will.

646
00:37:39,900 --> 00:37:40,860
Are you leaving?

647
00:37:42,740 --> 00:37:43,580
Yes.

648
00:37:44,900 --> 00:37:46,580
I am relieved now

649
00:37:48,260 --> 00:37:49,420
when I know that you are doing well.

650
00:37:50,740 --> 00:37:51,580
So,

651
00:37:52,740 --> 00:37:53,620
I won't disturb you anymore.

652
00:37:55,380 --> 00:37:56,420
You and Ziqing.

653
00:37:58,060 --> 00:37:59,020
Take good care of yourselves.

654
00:38:02,020 --> 00:38:02,860
Wait a moment.

655
00:38:15,900 --> 00:38:17,180
At your age now,

656
00:38:20,140 --> 00:38:21,820
