to wander the world anymore.

657
00:38:25,500 --> 00:38:27,140
Why not come back to Tianque with us?

658
00:38:34,580 --> 00:38:35,420
Alright.

659
00:38:36,780 --> 00:38:37,980
I will go back with you.

660
00:38:40,700 --> 00:38:41,820
I'm always thinking about

661
00:38:43,140 --> 00:38:44,700
reuniting with you.

662
00:38:47,100 --> 00:38:47,940
Beiyue,

663
00:38:49,820 --> 00:38:50,900
