667
00:39:29,740 --> 00:39:30,780
No need, Ziqing.

668
00:39:30,780 --> 00:39:31,700
I'm not hungry.

669
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:32,900
We should focus on our journey.

670
00:39:33,940 --> 00:39:36,220
Madam, you don't have to be so polite.

671
