684
00:40:16,660 --> 00:40:17,500
Alright.

685
00:40:18,420 --> 00:40:19,780
You two are thoughtful.

686
00:40:20,700 --> 00:40:21,620
I agree.

687
00:40:21,620 --> 00:40:22,460
Alright.

688
00:40:39,540 --> 00:40:42,300
