- Ziqing.

708
00:41:33,140 --> 00:41:34,980
The guest rooms are ready for you.

709
00:41:34,980 --> 00:41:35,820
Stop acting.

710
00:41:37,180 --> 00:41:38,020
Quickly.

711
00:41:39,900 --> 00:41:41,100
Sometimes,

712
00:41:42,420 --> 00:41:43,900
I wish we were outside.

713
00:41:45,700 --> 00:41:47,060
