722
00:42:06,900 --> 00:42:08,060
to call her mother?

723
00:42:17,300 --> 00:42:18,140
It's nothing.

724
00:42:20,340 --> 00:42:21,460
It's just a random talk.

725
00:42:23,740 --> 00:42:24,580
Good night.

726
00:42:25,460 --> 00:42:26,420
Good night.

